Jake Shorrocks (born 26 October 1995) is a rugby league footballer who plays as a scrum-half for the Wigan Warriors in the Betfred Super League.He has spent time on loan from Wigan at Workington Town and the Swinton Lions in the Championship, and the Salford Red Devils in the Super League.


== Background ==
Shorrocks was born in Wigan, Greater Manchester, England.


